Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: President Carter inaugurated
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407bpz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Jan 1977
President Carter's inauguration day spared the earlier snowstorms. Ground-breaking solar energy plan to warm the crowds fails to work. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less